### ==========================================================
### Activity Service — 2 requests
### Cursor-based pagination: first page, then use nextCursor
### ==========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@accessToken = <paste-after-login>
@nextCursor = <paste-from-first-feed-response>

### 1. Get activity feed (first page)
# Returns items from your friends' activity
# Response includes nextCursor and hasMore for pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/activity/feed?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Get activity feed (next page)
# Copy nextCursor from the previous response
GET {{baseUrl}}/activity/feed?cursor={{nextCursor}}&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
